  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink16-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">vāyilāyp pukuntārkkut tōḻi ‘avaṉ varavaiyē niṉaittu ivaḷ kaṇṇum pacantaṉa;
          iṉi avaṉ vantu peṟuvatu eṉṉai?’ eṉac colli vāyil maṟuttatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink16">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> ōṅkupū vēḻattut tūmpuṭait tiraḷkāṟ</l>
          <l> ciṟutoḻu makaḷi rañcaṉam peyyum</l>
          <l> pūkkaña lūraṉai yuḷḷip</l>
          <l> pūppō luṇkaṇ poṉpōrt taṉavē. </l>


        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> Remembering the man from the village dense with flowers,</l>
          <l rend='indent2'> where little maid-servants put on kajal</l>
          <l rend='indent2'> [using] the hollow, round stems of high, flowering wild-cane,</l>
          <l> [My] flower-like kajal eyes are wrapped in gold.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
